appear confused and indistinct.

01:11.517 --> 01:14.621
A strange multiplicity
of sensations seized me.

01:14.720 --> 01:19.492
And I saw, felt, heard
and smelled at the same time.

01:19.591 --> 01:23.063
And it was indeed a long time
before I learned to distinguish

01:23.162 --> 01:25.870
