Mannish boy!

1:08:25.814 --> 1:08:29.557
Are you a man or are you an animal?

1:08:31.219 --> 1:08:33.290
You fucking animal!

1:08:42.363 --> 1:08:43.467
Eddie.

1:08:50.004 --> 1:08:52.211
Eddie. Love.

1:08:54.342 --> 1:08:56.083
Eddie. Love.

1:09:22.737 --> 1:09:24.978
Eddie!

1:09:26.207 --> 1:09:27.811
Eddie!

1:09:29.644 --> 1:09:31.380
Eddie!

1:09:31.479 --> 1:09:34.016
Once I falsely hoped to meet with beings

1:09:34.115 --> 1:09:38.689
who, pardoning my outward form,
would love me for the qualities in my heart.

1:09:40.355 --> 1:09:42.224
I cannot believe
that I'm the same creature

1:09:42.323 --> 1:09:45.202
whose thoughts were once
filled with beauty and love.

1:09:59.674 --> 1:10:03.145
Starting route to 26800
Mulholland Highway.

1:10:03.244 --> 1:10:05.314
Tum left onto West 7th Street.

1:10:05.413 --> 1:10:06.382
Hey!

1:10:17.158 --> 1:10:20.264
In 400 feet, turn left
onto South Broadway.

1:10:26.201 --> 1:10:29.472
Keep right to merge onto CA 110 North.

1:10:32.006 --> 1:10:34.710
Hey, you can't walk here. Stop.

1:10:39.581 --> 1:10:41.217
- Stop. Stop right there.
- In 500 feet,

1:10:41.316 --> 1:10:44.786
keep right to merge onto CA 110 North.

1:10:46.621 --> 1:10:49.258
Stop. You can't walk here.

1:10:49.357 --> 1:10:51.026
Stop right there.

1:10:51.125 --> 1:10:53.366
Sir, stop! I said stop.

1:10:53.928 --> 1:10:54.929
Stop.

1:11:02.036 --> 1:11:03.515
What the fuck?

