1:11:47.949 --> 1:11:50.119
In 9.8 miles, keep right

1:11:50.218 --> 1:11:54.098
to merge onto US 101 North
towards Ventura.

1:11:54.489 --> 1:11:56.526
I will revenge my injuries.

1:11:57.959 --> 1:12:00.098
If I cannot inspire love,

1:12:01.129 --> 1:12:02.831
I will cause fear.

1:12:02.930 --> 1:12:07.879
In 19.6 miles, take exit 32
onto Las Virgenes Road.

1:12:22.417 --> 1:12:24.260
You have reached your destination.

1:13:52.707 --> 1:13:54.576
I don't know what's wrong with that guy.

1:14:07.688 --> 1:14:09.224
Sit on the bed.

1:14:12.360 --> 1:14:15.164
Now here comes Dr. Feelgood.

1:14:21.402 --> 1:14:22.972
I love you so much.

1:14:53.468 --> 1:14:54.913
Oh, what's happened?

1:14:56.370 --> 1:14:57.439
Don't hurt him.

1:14:57.538 --> 1:14:58.573
No!

1:14:59.674 --> 1:15:01.517
No! No!

1:15:04.345 --> 1:15:06.484
- Let him go. Let him go.
- Mine!

1:15:06.981 --> 1:15:08.016
Why?

1:15:12.186 --> 1:15:16.498
You said you did not know me.

1:15:17.091 --> 1:15:18.661
I ugly.

1:15:19.627 --> 1:15:20.662
Stop!

1:15:20.761 --> 1:15:22.206
- No.
- Stop. Leave her.

1:15:22.830 --> 1:15:23.831
No.

1:15:24.899 --> 1:15:26.268
It's okay.

1:15:26.367 --> 1:15:28.278
It's okay, Adam.

1:15:29.170 --> 1:15:30.478
I'm sorry.

1:15:30.805 --> 1:15:33.046
- Adam?
- Yes.

1:15:33.841 --> 1:15:36.651
Your name is Adam.

1:16:27.094 --> 1:16:29.404
See? That's how we made you.

1:16:31.432 --> 1:16:33.535
- And we'll make you again.
- No.

1:16:33.634 --> 1:16:34.840
Oh, no, yes.

1:16:36.337 --> 1:16:37.372
Yes.

1:16:38.739 --> 1:16:41.879
And this time you'll be beautiful.

1:16:43.744 --> 1:16:45.246
Beautiful.

1:16:55.323 --> 1:16:56.393
Oh.

1:16:58.459 --> 1:17:01.963
You make me

1:17:04.165 --> 1:17:05.303
ugly.

1:17:09.003 --> 1:17:10.209
Why?

1:17:11.272 --> 1:17:14.109
I don't know. It was a mistake.

1:17:14.208 --> 1:17:16.711
The cells didn't replicate correctly,

1:17:17.645 --> 1:17:20.082
and God only knows
what turned you into such a vicious beast.

1:17:20.181 --> 1:17:21.182
Victor.

1:17:22.984 --> 1:17:26.693
He is not me.

1:17:28.022 --> 1:17:29.958
Not me.

1:17:30.057 --> 1:17:32.037
He is...

1:17:35.863 --> 1:17:36.832
Other.

1:17:36.931 --> 1:17:39.036
- He is exactly like you.
- No.

1:17:40.267 --> 1:17:42.873
I am

1:17:49.176 --> 1:17:50.479
I.

1:17:50.578 --> 1:17:52.080
Yes.

1:17:52.179 --> 1:17:54.352
And you will be you again.

1:17:56.550 --> 1:18:00.794
My boy, I understand your unhappiness.

1:18:01.989 --> 1:18:03.866
I understand your pain.

1:18:04.859 --> 1:18:07.465
And I can make it go away.

1:18:09.630 --> 1:18:13.077
You will close your eyes
and you will sleep.

1:18:14.335 --> 1:18:16.772
And when you wake up,

1:18:16.871 --> 1:18:19.044
you'll be just fine.

1:18:30.184 --> 1:18:33.631
He is dead?

1:18:34.355 --> 1:18:36.335
He's nothing but clay.

1:18:37.525 --> 1:18:40.768
But we can all breathe life into him.

1:18:43.197 --> 1:18:47.043
You see, that is the secret
that God is so jealous of.

1:18:48.302 --> 1:18:49.679
The formula for life.

1:18:50.471 --> 1:18:53.816
And I, me, Dr. Frankenstein,

1:18:55.543 --> 1:18:56.945
discovered it,

1:18:57.044 --> 1:18:58.648
and I will do it again.

1:19:25.106 --> 1:19:26.585
No!

1:19:28.375 --> 1:19:30.582
I am!

1:19:42.957 --> 1:19:45.198
I am.

1:19:45.626 --> 1:19:48.072
I am.

1:19:48.562 --> 1:19:50.735
I am. I am.

1:19:51.232 --> 1:19:54.702
I am.

1:19:56.670 --> 1:19:57.910
You.

1:19:58.706 --> 1:20:00.777
You made me.

1:20:04.478 --> 1:20:06.115
You

1:20:07.509 --> 1:20:09.598
hate me.

1:20:09.898 --> 1:20:11.088
No.

1:20:16.857 --> 1:20:20.828
I'm alone.

1:20:24.465 --> 1:20:27.049
I'm

1:20:28.146 --> 1:20:30.046
alone.

1:20:50.658 --> 1:20:52.961
I'll decapitate him
and then incinerate his head.

1:20:53.060 --> 1:20:54.329
- Get off.
- No.

1:20:54.428 --> 1:20:55.430
- Move.
- I can't.

1:20:55.529 --> 1:20:56.765
Don't be ridiculous.

1:21:08.475 --> 1:21:10.284
No. Oh.

1:21:11.579 --> 1:21:14.059
Oh, my God. Oh, no.

1:22:36.263 --> 1:22:42.077
I shall collect my funeral pile and consume
to ashes this miserable frame.

1:22:43.637 --> 1:22:47.909
That its remains may afford no light
to any curious and unhallowed wretch

1:22:48.008 --> 1:22:50.454
who would create such another
as I have been.

1:22:57.584 --> 1:22:59.962
She is dead, who called me into being.

1:23:01.088 --> 1:23:03.625
When I shall be no more,

1:23:03.724 --> 1:23:06.898
the very remembrance of us both
will speedily vanish.

1:23:07.494 --> 1:23:10.737
I will no longer see the sun nor stars,

1:23:11.565 --> 1:23:13.909
or feel the winds play upon my cheeks.

1:23:14.668 --> 1:23:17.512
I shall ascend
my funeral pile triumphantly

1:23:19.473 --> 1:23:22.181
and exalt in the agony
of the torturing flames.

1:23:24.311 --> 1:23:26.951
The light of that conflagration
will fade away.

1:23:28.082 --> 1:23:31.086
My ashes will be swept into the sea
by the winds.

1:23:32.152 --> 1:23:34.359
My spirit will sleep in peace.

1:23:35.489 --> 1:23:39.232
Or if it thinks,
it will not surely think thus.

1:23:41.862 --> 1:23:43.068
Farewell.

1:24:31.078 --> 1:24:36.050
I am Adam!
